              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-white text-primary-700 px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-semibold hover:bg-gray-50 transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105 shadow-lg"
            >
              Get a Free Consultation with our Preferred Partner
