              </svg>
            </button>
            <p class="text-xs text-white/70 mt-3">Our relocation partners work with us and provide free consultations to all users</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Why Strategic Advisory Matters -->
        <div class="mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Why Strategic Advisory Matters for Complex Relocations</h2>
          <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-4">
            <p>
              Switzerland offers <strong>exceptional opportunities for entrepreneurs, investors, and high-net-worth individuals</strong>, 
              but navigating the regulatory landscape requires strategic expertise. Unlike standard relocations, complex moves involving 
              substantial wealth, business operations, or corporate transfers demand comprehensive planning to optimize outcomes and mitigate risks.
            </p>
            <p>
              <strong>Cantonal tax variations, regulatory complexity, and permit nuances</strong> create significant challenges. 
