            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 to-primary-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Personal & Family Relocations</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">
                <strong>Premium advisory for entrepreneurs, investors, and pensioners</strong> relocating to Switzerland. We structure 
                self-employed permits, investor residence applications, lump-sum taxation arrangements, and wealth transfer strategies. 
                Includes <a href="/services/housing" class="text-primary-600 hover:underline">luxury housing search</a> and family support.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 to-primary-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
