                compliance. Ideal for entrepreneurs seeking tax-efficient structures, crypto startups requiring regulatory clarity, and 
                HNWI optimizing their wealth management through Swiss-based holding structures.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Basel – Pharma & Cross-Border Advisory</h3>
