                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Optimization & Long-Term Review</h4>
                  <p class="text-gray-700">
                    Ongoing strategic review to optimize your Swiss presence including tax efficiency assessment, permit progression 
                    planning (B to C permit), investment structuring adjustments, and compliance monitoring. Annual reviews ensure 
                    your relocation continues to deliver maximum value and adapts to changing regulations or personal circumstances.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </li>
