              <li class="flex gap-3">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                </svg>
                <p class="text-gray-800"><strong>Corporate relocation policies:</strong> Structured policies reduce risk, ensure compliance, control costs, and provide duty of care for employee transfers</p>
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-3">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
